title: Bump jQuery.Validation from 1.17.0 to 1.19.3 in /samples/Basic/Web/SkiaSharpSample
body:
Bumps jQuery.Validation from 1.17.0 to 1.19.3. [![Dependabot compatibility score](https://dependabot-badges.githubapp.com/badges/compatibility_score?dependency-name=jQuery.Validation&package-manager=nuget&previous-version=1.17.0&new-version=1.19.3)](https://docs.github.com/en/github/managing-security-vulnerabilities/about-dependabot-security-updates#about-compatibility-scores) Dependabot will resolve any conflicts with this PR as long as you don't alter it yourself. You can also trigger a rebase manually by commenting `@dependabot rebase`. [//]: # (dependabot-automerge-start) [//]: # (dependabot-automerge-end) ---
